these ones are fine because they provide a percentage
the #s under the commander need some rank context i think
maybe Rank in color identity and overall rank, maybe for past 6 months
card pages :

they tell you the count but they don't take into account how many decks have that commander
so for example, entreat the angels is much more important to avacyn (higher %) but it shows animatou as #1 simply because there are so many more decks
